getLastError() to get the error code.
For more details, refer to Troubleshooting.
.SH HISTORY
.PP
v2.0 and above
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Create a catalog replication group on the host named "hostname1", specify the
service port as 11800, specify the data file storage path as
\f[C]/opt/sequoiadb/database/cata/11800\f[], and configure the log file size as
64MB.
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> db.createCataRG("hostname1",11800,"/opt/sequoiadb/database/cata/11800",{logfilesz:64})
\f[]
